  "instructions": [
    "preheat the oven to 375°f (190°c).",
    "in a food processor, mash the chickpeas, fennel seeds, coriander powder, cumin powder, paprika, garlic, and ginger until well combined.",
    "add lemon juice, olive oil, agave syrup, and ferment jang to the food processor and process until smooth.",
    "using your hands, shape the mixture into small falafel patties.",
    "heat a non-stick skillet over medium heat and fry the falafel patties until golden brown on both sides.",
    "transfer the falafel patties to a baking sheet and bake in the preheated oven for 15 minutes.",
    "serve the falafel patties in agave leaves with additional ferment jang if desired."
  ],
